Dialogue: 0,0:00:-14.00,0:00:-06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'll we save Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:06.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:17.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:30.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:35.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:53.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.39,0:01:12.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.80,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.82,0:01:27.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:34.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:39.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:41.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:45.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:53.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:00.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:12.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:14.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:18.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:25.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:32.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were confronted by the\NAccino Family bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew dodged the Accino Family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and managed to get the Sunny\Noutside of the Arctic Path once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to lose their Jolly Roger,\Nthe embodiment of their pirate souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the flapping Jolly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Jolly Roger is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret behind the\NArctic Path's moving icebergs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were the peculiar Savage Penguins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Straw Hat Pirates\Nhave been split up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Accino Family is swooping\Nin to claim their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your luck bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Blend-sama, the second \Nson in the Accino Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Desperate Battles for the Straw Hat Crew!\NPinning Their Pirate Souls on the Flag"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lovely Land"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your flag is in Lovely Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Accino Family's base of operations\Nis none other than Lovely Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you see cuffed pirates smile\Nas they're handed to the Marines?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was still in the middle of my explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught me off guard a second ago--whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your captain isn't too bright, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder you lost\Nyour precious Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ex-pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready for the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to see Hell,\Nall because you covered
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for that pathetic excuse of a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dilly-dally, who knows what\Nwill happen to the flag we stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd let him attack me until \Nhe wore himself out and screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he isn't showing any openings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, his openings are getting smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a cute ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Thousand Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I see you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when you\Nshowed up so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Lil, do you know where\Nthe rest of the crew is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thousand's crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know where your flag went!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you searching for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister hasn't been\Nplaying with me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always playing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always with that creepy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Salchow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking truly terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're launching an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just circling around us \Nover and over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump and kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell, the rink today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is perfect for... skating on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump and kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Salchow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think... we're going to \Nget... some good skating in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't gonna let us \Nup and leave, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we need to hurry back to the Sunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do something about these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell-chan, that's sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're super easy on the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just how he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're super sassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who stole \Nour flag, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell, you're nice even on the rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you put that flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La la-la la!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Papa-san would be tickled pink
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we finished these two off\Nand brought back their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, Salchow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that was enough for our warm-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Our heads?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So they really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbe--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady is flying into my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he sent a lady flying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a vile thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guy from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy who stole\Nour Jolly Roger, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Jolly Roger got stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who coulda done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're wasting our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, this place is too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quit the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Family stole your flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The location?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually do know where your flag is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, where was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gettin' nowhere fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had projectiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't how real men fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shoulda played nice and told me\Nyou packed that stuff from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cold for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send him flying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the game begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's my projectiles versus yours,\NI'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This defeats the point of my winter outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to lose visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was just goofing off,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll never get anywhere if\NI can't see where I'm shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the cold is starting to numb my movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to finish this fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time if \Nyou can't see your target!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play with an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You found me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which hand is the coin in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Lil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is our flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our flags are in Papa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a whole bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His room is covered with Jolly Rogers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is his birthday, so everyone\Ncame to pick up a birthday present!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the flag the present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person has a 300-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one has a 120-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one has a 44-million-Berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have an 80-million-Berry \Nbounty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your flag all that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That flag represents our pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means nothing to a raccoon like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking pirate talk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you'll get off lightly for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could a raccoon possibly hope to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the feisty one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you take me down,\Nbut what will you do about your flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me out, who will\Nguide you to Lovely Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for directions after I whack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose a 300-million-Berry bounty\Nwon't go down without a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be safest if I threw in the towel for now\Nand finished them off at Lovely Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me a--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give back my Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm raising the white flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have your flag right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand it over now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give our Jolly Roger back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to come after me\Nif you want the real flag back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for you ex-pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who stole our Jolly Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've incurred the wrath of the almighty\NUsopp-sama, you stupid doting couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Flame Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull's eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens to the fools\Nwho damage a pirate's pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were really in the groove!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna break your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy fell into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it all for their Jolly Roger...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do that if he couldn't swim...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you can't swim either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to set \Nsail without the Jolly Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, go look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's about time you put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in an uproar, claiming that\Nthe Jolly Roger "went missing."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the King of the \NPirates under this Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of hearing that, \Nbut I have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes you the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone can defeat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the Phoenix's Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, that was pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna run from a fight,\Nyou should give up being pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just goes to show how powerful \Nthis Jolly Roger has grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't caught them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the Straw Hats' flag coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be here soon, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say that you enjoy things more\Nif you have to wait for them, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone pass by just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't notice anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had too much to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, hurry up with the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see how it's coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also check on Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best part of a game is the brawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at those, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game set...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right when I ran outta cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda cramped in here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept you waiting, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to lend you a hand\Nand tried pressing some buttons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing would turn on and it's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pounding won't stop and \Nthe temperature keeps dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pounding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught them alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my kites, Uo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's resume our game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My third oldest brother\Ncaught two of the bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we play some more at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come to my house to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you invite me over?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there two of the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a Devil Fruit power holder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clone technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no objections!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stifling to the Max!\NThe Twins' Magnetic Power Looms"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
